name: Ivanti ITSM
description: This app integrates with Ivanti ITSM to provide ingestion and several ticketing actions

poll_now_ingestion_span.description: Poll last n days for 'Poll Now'

first_scheduled_ingestion_span.description: Poll last n days for first scheduled polling

actions.description: Validate the asset configuration for connectivity using supplied configuration

actions.verbose:
Certain fields are required to create a ticket on Help Desk. Those fields are represented by the required parameters for this action.

The customer parameter takes a Customer Record ID, which can be found by running a list users or a get user action.

The fields parameter takes a JSON dictionary containing other fields and values that can be set during ticket creation. For example:
{
"Impact": "High"
"Urgency": "Medium"
}

The attachment parameter takes a vault ID.

attachment.description: Vault ID of file to attach
